{"tid":2090545,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教學：找出潛藏你facebook中嘅藍絲，以防篤灰","createTime":"2020-07-02T08:24:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T08:42:11.000Z","uid":288107,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6555dd238197b0facef0aa9c2da6de39b4a3cd1d","tid":2090545,"uid":288107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:24:19.000Z","msg":"有用開假fb acc滲透藍絲fb群組嘅人就會知<br />\n藍絲篤灰起底再向僱主或国安舉報言論，其實日日都發生<br />\n<br />\n国安法日後以言入罪，只要唔係明確支持政府嘅人，都係不能幸免<br />\n唔好以為你唔寫口號、言辭隱晦就安全，就算係一句「我好撚鐘意香港」都係一個風險<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我近日發現，原來如果用真實fb acc入一d大嘅藍絲group</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">例如save hk、香港行動HKAT</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">就會發現一堆你平時唔察覺嘅fb朋友原來都係喺group入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JZjHKsZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJZjHKsZ.png&h=4d045071&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n(用我假acc截圖做例子，名字唔洗打格）<br />\n<br />\n排除一d明顯係黃、因做記者入去滲透嘅朋友之外<br />\n就發現其他在group內嘅朋友大多數無乜喺社交網站活動，你甚至可能唔記得佢係你朋友<br />\n但原來佢係<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span></strong>絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知有幾多你曾經po過嘅黃野佢地可能已經cap起留底<br />\n最大問題係，呢d人可能係你現實生活中認識，佢已經知你真名係咩、住邊區，因此即使你fb名轉左、hide哂你d相，佢地都可輕易篤你出來<br />\n<br />\n不幸嘅係，呢個方法一定要用真實fb account先做到，你可能要隱藏你嘅黃profile pic或者cover photo先可以成功申請進入，但一般應該係好易批。而一但入左group，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">就千祈唔好留言甚至比like</span></strong>，以免曝露身份。<br />\n<br />\n當你加入藍絲group，發現左呢班人之後，你就可以：<br />\n1. 刪除或封鎖<br />\n2. 加入限制朋友名單，令佢地只可見到你嘅地球po、或者加入自訂朋友名單，令佢地只可以睇到你某d 自己選擇嘅 po<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WHzsVzW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWHzsVzW.png&h=aab287a1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hCNKdrJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhCNKdrJ.png&h=05dfbb85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AARnKys.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAARnKys.png&h=5ee98468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 在群組內搜尋藍絲曾經po過嘅言論，cap低存檔。例如你會發現好多人原來支持一d你唔會以為佢平時會講嘅野，例如支持不需審訊入罪、支持槍殺手足、支持封殺所有傳媒記者、支持吊銷所有黃醫護牌照等等。日後香港重光嘅時候，呢班人一定會見風駛舵，cap底嘅就可以攞出嚟做證據。同時我亦可以記錄下當年今日，就係呢d人支持打壓我和所有香港人嘅自由同權利 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FH41fET.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFH41fET.png&h=118d14a3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3HHNVET.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3HHNVET.png&h=5b2821f3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LnEHKye.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLnEHKye.png&h=d16013b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n4. 而我個係會繼績留喺群組內，因為呢d朋友一喺群組內留言，就會優先在你fb feed上顯示。而因為我對呢d野特別記仇，我會繼績cap底佢哋係藍絲群組嘅活動，不過你是否選擇留低就你自己決定嘞<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"7d59609ed39e1a4a0da43e06ec68bcfa501abc6c","tid":2090545,"uid":74083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa060398eda1822eca74b0c6d10e119e9fc229b2","tid":2090545,"uid":188374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:30:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8522a7fe25e83e622af56f648de69e67f68918e5","tid":2090545,"uid":354581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9YdEMTs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9YdE